      • getAllEnclosedExecutableElements

        public static List<ExecutableElement> getAllEnclosedExecutableElements(Elements elementUtils,
                                                                       TypeElement element)
        Finds all executable elements within the given type element, including executable elements defined in super classes and implemented interfaces. Methods defined in Object are ignored, as well as implementations of Object.equals(Object).
        Parameters:
        elementUtils - element helper
        element - the element to inspect
        Returns:
        the executable elements usable in the type
